snippet.title: fault - milestone two side: below - Exclusive Japanese Trailer | TGS 2020
snippet.description: Check out the latest trailer for fault - milestone two side: below! This cinematic adventure is the third in the highly acclaimed fault series of cinematic science fantasy novels. Coming to Steam, Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4.
